QuestData.Title: Sethe, the Dead God
QuestData.Description: The time has come to put an end to Sethe. I killed him before, and with your help I shall do it again.$B$BReady yourself for a fight - the cultists will not stand idly by while we stamp out their god.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Reborn at the hands of the Sethekk.
QuestData.LogDescription: Help Anzu defeat Sethe in the Broken Spire.
QuestData.RewardText: Sethe has died twice, but his curse lives on. It seems we will never be rid of it.
